query:
SELECT d.id, d.regency_id
                FROM districts d
                WHERE d.regency_id = $3
                  AND (d.name ILIKE $1
                       OR d.name ILIKE $2
                       OR d.name ILIKE '%' || $1 || '%')
                ORDER BY
                    CASE
                        WHEN d.name ILIKE $1 THEN 1
                        WHEN d.name ILIKE $2 THEN 2
                        ELSE 3
                    END
                LIMIT 1
